  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the iron teppan vessel over medium high heat",
    "Add olive oil and saute the chopped onion and bell pepper until tender",
    "Add the chopped tomato and cook for an additional 2 minutes",
    "Add the fish stock, smoked paprika, and lime juice, stirring to combine",
    "Add the cod fillets and cook for 4 minutes per side, or until cooked through",
    "Top the cod fillets with shredded Brazilian cheese and cook until melted and bubbly",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot",
    "Cook the dish for an additional 2 minutes to ensure the cheese is melted and bubbly"
